            "\u001b[34mGmsh, a 3D mesh generator with pre- and post-processing facilities\u001b[0m\n",
            "\u001b[34mCopyright (C) 1997-2021 C. Geuzaine and J.-F. Remacle\u001b[0m\n",
            "\u001b[34mUsage: gmsh [options] [files]\u001b[0m\n",
            "\u001b[34m(Related option names, if any, are given between parentheses)\u001b[0m\n",
            "\u001b[34mGeometry:\u001b[0m\n",
            "\u001b[34m  -0                   Output model, then exit\u001b[0m\n",
            "\u001b[34m  -tol value           Set geometrical tolerance (Geometry.Tolerance)\u001b[0m\n",
            "\u001b[34m  -match               Match geometries and meshes\u001b[0m\n",
            "\u001b[34mMesh:\u001b[0m\n",
            "\u001b[34m  -1, -2, -3           Perform 1D, 2D or 3D mesh generation, then exit\u001b[0m\n",
            "\u001b[34m  -save                Save mesh, then exit\u001b[0m\n",
            "\u001b[34m  -o file              Specify output file name\u001b[0m\n",
            "\u001b[34m  -format string       Select output mesh format: auto, msh1, msh2, msh22, msh3, msh4, msh40, msh41, msh, unv, vtk, wrl, mail, stl, p3d, mesh, bdf, cgns, med, diff, ir3, inp, ply2, celum, su2, x3d, dat, neu, m, key (Mesh.Format)\u001b[0m\n",
            "\u001b[34m  -bin                 Create binary files when possible (Mesh.Binary)\u001b[0m\n",
            "\u001b[34m  -refine              Perform uniform mesh refinement, then exit\u001b[0m\n",
            "\u001b[34m  -barycentric_refine  Perform barycentric mesh refinement, then exit\u001b[0m\n",
            "\u001b[34m  -reclassify angle    Reclassify surface mesh, then exit\u001b[0m\n",
            "\u001b[34m  -reparam angle       Reparametrize surface mesh, then exit\u001b[0m\n",
            "\u001b[34m  -part int            Partition after batch mesh generation (Mesh.NbPartitions)\u001b[0m\n",
            "\u001b[34m  -part_weight [tri,quad,tet,hex,pri,pyr,trih] int Weight of a triangle/quad/etc. during partitioning (Mesh.Partition[Tri,Quad,...]Weight)\u001b[0m\n",
            "\u001b[34m  -part_split          Save mesh partitions in separate files (Mesh.PartitionSplitMeshFiles)\u001b[0m\n",
            "\u001b[34m  -part_[no_]topo      Create the partition topology (Mesh.PartitionCreateTopology)\u001b[0m\n",
            "\u001b[34m  -part_[no_]ghosts    Create ghost cells (Mesh.PartitionCreateGhostCells)\u001b[0m\n",
            "\u001b[34m  -part_[no_]physicals Create physical groups for partitions (Mesh.PartitionCreatePhysicals)\u001b[0m\n",
